{"id": 57667, "date": "2025-07-12T04:00:39", "date_gmt": "2025-07-12T11:00:39", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57667"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T10:22:16", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T17:22:16", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-12-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/12/kingdom-of-days-july-12-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 12"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1968:\u00a0</strong>The Castiles headline a gig at the Hullabaloo in Freehold.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"2995\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1968-0712/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0712.jpg?fit=443%2C250&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"443,250\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1968-0712\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0712.jpg?fit=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0712.jpg?fit=443%2C250&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2995 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0712.jpg?resize=443%2C250&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"443\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0712.jpg?w=443&amp;ssl=1 443w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0712.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 443px) 100vw, 443px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1972:\u00a0</strong>Bruce is at 914 Sound Studios in Blauvelt for a mixing session for his debut album.</p>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band headline two shows at The Bottom Line in New York City. There&#8217;s an early performance (likely the earliest) of a\u00a0<em>very</em> work-in-progress &#8220;Jungleland&#8221; that is believed to be from this show. It&#8217;s well worth a listen, as it&#8217;s dramatically different from the final version that will be released on vinyl over a year later.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZdUS8iqQiiM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-57667-8\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/02a-Kittys-Back.mp3?_=8\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/02a-Kittys-Back.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/02a-Kittys-Back.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"68250\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/12/kingdom-of-days-july-12-2/newsday_nassau_edition__1974_07_15_87-scaled/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Newsday_Nassau_Edition__1974_07_15_87-scaled-1.jpg?fit=701%2C1810&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"701,1810\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Newsday_Nassau_Edition__1974_07_15_87-scaled\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Newsday_Nassau_Edition__1974_07_15_87-scaled-1.jpg?fit=116%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Newsday_Nassau_Edition__1974_07_15_87-scaled-1.jpg?fit=397%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-68250\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Newsday_Nassau_Edition__1974_07_15_87-scaled-1.jpg?resize=701%2C1810&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"701\" height=\"1810\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Newsday_Nassau_Edition__1974_07_15_87-scaled-1.jpg?w=701&amp;ssl=1 701w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Newsday_Nassau_Edition__1974_07_15_87-scaled-1.jpg?resize=116%2C300&amp;ssl=1 116w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Newsday_Nassau_Edition__1974_07_15_87-scaled-1.jpg?resize=397%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 397w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Newsday_Nassau_Edition__1974_07_15_87-scaled-1.jpg?resize=595%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 595w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 701px) 100vw, 701px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band work on &#8220;Frankie&#8221; during a recording session at Atlantic Studios in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the boys bring the Darkness Tour to Dallas, where poor ticket sales force the show to be moved from the 10,000-seat Convention Center Arena to the 1,700-seat Convention Center Theater instead. Because fans have to exchange their tickets on the way in, it takes a long time to admit everyone, and you can hear Bruce ask fans for their patience before the show starts below.</p>\n<div id=\"v-nfXyYNHm-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/nfXyYNHm?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19484\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-07-12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-12.jpg?fit=854%2C958&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"854,958\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593183457&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-07-12\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-12.jpg?fit=267%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-12.jpg?fit=758%2C850&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19484 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-12.jpg?resize=758%2C850&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"850\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-12.jpg?w=854&amp;ssl=1 854w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-12.jpg?resize=267%2C300&amp;ssl=1 267w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-07-12.jpg?resize=768%2C862&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band work on &#8220;I Wanna Marry You&#8221; during a recording session at the Power Station in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>The Born in the U.S.A. Tour continues its midwest trek, arriving in East Troy, Wisconsin for the first of two nights. This show is notable for the world debut of the very rare &#8220;Man at the Top&#8221; (played only twice since). According to press reports, director Brian De Palma shoots additional footage for &#8220;Dancing in the Dark&#8221; at this show. It&#8217;s unclear if any of it will be used.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/N7s0WtNiTHI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wzfUSuyrWLA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2Qu3z3_7svw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"68251\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/12/kingdom-of-days-july-12-2/1984-07-12a-rotated/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1984-07-12a-rotated-1.jpg?fit=460%2C987&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"460,987\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-07-12a-rotated\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1984-07-12a-rotated-1.jpg?fit=140%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1984-07-12a-rotated-1.jpg?fit=460%2C987&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-68251\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1984-07-12a-rotated-1.jpg?resize=460%2C987&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"460\" height=\"987\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1984-07-12a-rotated-1.jpg?w=460&amp;ssl=1 460w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1984-07-12a-rotated-1.jpg?resize=140%2C300&amp;ssl=1 140w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19486\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-07-12b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-12b.jpg?fit=1252%2C774&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1252,774\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593184143&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-07-12b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-12b.jpg?fit=300%2C185&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-12b.jpg?fit=758%2C469&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19486 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-12b.jpg?resize=758%2C469&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"469\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-12b.jpg?w=1252&amp;ssl=1 1252w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-12b.jpg?resize=300%2C185&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-12b.jpg?resize=1024%2C633&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-12b.jpg?resize=768%2C475&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1988:\u00a0</strong>The Tunnel of Love Tour continues its final leg, stopping in Frankfurt for one show.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJTyL9twk3zDyj6Y8J4-wFBZXiAdDa7AE\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1991:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Bobby Bandiera on stage for five songs at McLoone&#8217;s Rum Runner in Sea Bright, New Jersey.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-57667-9\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1991-07-12__Merged.mp3?_=9\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1991-07-12__Merged.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1991-07-12__Merged.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>Night Four of five at Wembley Arena for Bruce&#8217;s World Tour 1992. The setlist highlight: &#8220;The Big Muddy,&#8221; played only twice in Europe.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cGolb8D4DkY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/N3ZL-rRo_hQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1994:\u00a0</strong>Joe Grushecky and Bruce record &#8220;Talk Show,&#8221; &#8220;Comin&#8217; Down Maria,&#8221; and &#8220;Only Lovers Left Alive&#8221; for Joe&#8217;s\u00a0<em>American Babylon</em> album at Bruce&#8217;s home studio in Rumson, New Jersey. Bruce plays uncredited on all three tracks, and Patti provides backing vocals for &#8220;Comin&#8217; Down Maria.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/d2OCZHh7w_0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WLshTQTt0Rg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_JGAd81f--4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band rehearse for the upcoming Rising Tour at the Expo Theater in Fort Monmouth, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"11236\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2002-07-12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2002-07-12.jpg?fit=426%2C287&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"426,287\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2002-07-12\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2002-07-12.jpg?fit=300%2C202&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2002-07-12.jpg?fit=426%2C287&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11236 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2002-07-12.jpg?resize=426%2C287&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"426\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2002-07-12.jpg?w=426&amp;ssl=1 426w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2002-07-12.jpg?resize=300%2C202&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>At Night Two in Dublin on the Working on a Dream Tour, Bruce and the band perform the tour premiere of &#8220;American Skin (41 Shots).&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/eR1JwRAPnWE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4lqaAfLzs_M?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-t